WEBVTT

00:19.410 --> 00:21.673
WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE?

00:21.673 --> 00:23.110
I WAS IN THE NEIGHBORHOOD.

00:23.110 --> 00:24.633
THOUGHT YOU MIGHT NEED
A LIFT.

00:24.633 --> 00:26.809
NO, THAT'S OK.

00:26.809 --> 00:28.767
WELL, SOMETIMES REED
GIVES ME A RIDE

00:28.767 --> 00:30.117
ON HIS WAY OVER
TO GRIFFIN'S,

00:30.117 --> 00:31.553
SO...

00:31.553 --> 00:33.642
WHY DON'T
I CATCH YOU LATER AT HOME?

00:33.642 --> 00:34.904
ARE YOU SERIOUS?

00:34.904 --> 00:36.645
GET IN THE CAR,
CLAUD.

00:36.645 --> 00:37.689
COME ON, CHARLIE.

00:37.689 --> 00:38.908
GET IN THE CAR.

00:44.870 --> 00:48.004
LOOK, UM,
AS LONG AS WE'RE ALONE,

00:48.004 --> 00:49.745
I WANTED TO TALK
TO YOU ABOUT SOMETHING,

00:49.745 --> 00:52.748
SOMETHING THAT'S BEEN
GOING ON WITH ME.

00:52.748 --> 00:54.663
I HAVEN'T TOLD
THE OTHERS YET.

00:54.663 --> 00:56.665
I WANTED
TO TELL YOU FIRST.

01:00.495 --> 01:03.585
I'M KINDA, UM...

01:03.585 --> 01:07.284
IT TURNS OUT
I'VE GOT THIS--
THIS THING,

01:07.284 --> 01:10.722
THIS DISEASE THING.

01:10.722 --> 01:12.246
WHAT, LIKE V.D.
OR SOMETHING?

01:12.246 --> 01:13.769
CHARLIE.

01:13.769 --> 01:16.598
NO, IT'S NOT--
IT'S NOTHING LIKE THAT.

01:16.598 --> 01:21.646
IT'S CALLED HODGKIN'S.HODGKIN'S, I DON'T--

01:21.646 --> 01:24.736
IT'S A DISEASE
OF THE LYMPHATIC SYSTEM,

01:24.736 --> 01:28.262
AND SOMETIMES
IT TURNS UP IN GUYS
ABOUT MY AGE.

01:28.262 --> 01:31.787
THAT'S WHY I'VE BEEN
FEELING SO, YOU KNOW,

01:31.787 --> 01:33.745
KINDA DRAGGY
AND RUN DOWN

01:33.745 --> 01:35.878
FOR THE PAST FEW WEEKS.

01:35.878 --> 01:37.706
I THOUGHT
THAT WAS NO BIG DEAL.

01:37.706 --> 01:42.928
I KNOW. ME, TOO,
BUT I WENT TO SEE
THE DOCTOR,

01:42.928 --> 01:45.366
AND SHE DIAGNOSED IT
RIGHT AWAY,

01:45.366 --> 01:47.237
WHICH IS GREAT
BECAUSE IF IT'S
CAUGHT EARLY,

01:47.237 --> 01:49.674
WHICH MINE
DEFINITELY WAS,

01:49.674 --> 01:53.417
THEN THIS THING'S,
LIKE, 100% CURABLE.

01:53.417 --> 01:55.158
IT'S, LIKE,
100% CURABLE

01:55.158 --> 01:56.855
OR IT IS 100% CURABLE?

01:56.855 --> 01:58.770
I'M GOING TO BE FINE,
CLAUDIA.

01:58.770 --> 02:00.598
OK?

02:00.598 --> 02:02.383
I'M GOING TO HAVE TO HAVE
SOME TREATMENTS AND STUFF,

02:02.383 --> 02:05.647
WHICH JUST MEANS
GOING INTO THE DOCTOR'S
OFFICE EVERY DAY

02:05.647 --> 02:06.778
FOR, LIKE, 5 MINUTES.

02:06.778 --> 02:07.823
FOR WHAT, MEDICINE?

02:07.823 --> 02:10.304
YEAH. PRETTY MUCH.

02:10.304 --> 02:11.783
THEY JUST WANT
TO MAKE SURE

02:11.783 --> 02:13.611
THAT YOU'RE GETTING
THE RIGHT DOSAGE.

02:13.611 --> 02:15.918
IT TAKES 6 WEEKS,

02:15.918 --> 02:19.182
AND THEN IT'S OVER.

02:19.182 --> 02:21.837
I'M TOTALLY
BACK TO NORMAL.

02:24.622 --> 02:26.102
YOU KNOW WHAT
THE DOCTOR TOLD ME?

02:26.102 --> 02:28.887
SHE SAID
THAT IF YOU HAVE
TO HAVE A DISEASE,

02:28.887 --> 02:31.542
HODGKIN'S IS DEFINITELY
ONE OF THE BEST ONES
TO HAVE.

02:33.544 --> 02:34.806
THAT'S PRETTY
REASSURING, HUH?

02:36.634 --> 02:38.158
OK.

02:44.947 --> 02:46.775
HOW DOES ICE CREAM SOUND?

